Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.06,0:00:13.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然向我银之炼金术师朱利欧·科曼契挑战
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.07,0:00:15.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的胆量值得称赞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.87,0:00:16.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.32,0:00:53.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还挺行的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.12,0:00:55.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然只是擦到
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.67,0:00:59.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只擦到一点吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.63,0:02:50.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.99,0:02:52.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老爷 您回来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.35,0:02:54.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.02,0:02:56.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,初次见面
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.74,0:02:58.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫张梅
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.39,0:03:02.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,950)\fn方正大标宋_GBK\fs135\fsp12\blur6\bord5\1c&H00&\3c&HFFFFFFFF&}东方的使者
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.73,0:03:06.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次倒在路边的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.10,0:03:09.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被你的主人 尤基大人所救
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.13,0:03:11.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主人？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.93,0:03:15.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果好了的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.74,0:03:17.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就快点离开这里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.04,0:03:28.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.25,0:03:31.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来治疗伤口
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.42,0:03:48.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,治好了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.13,0:03:51.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是流传于清国的炼丹术
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.18,0:03:53.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,清国？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.71,0:03:54.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.18,0:03:59.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙一个人穿越了东边的大沙漠来到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.36,0:04:00.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.86,0:04:03.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.76,0:04:05.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是一个人和一只
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.51,0:04:10.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一只是指那个小东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.07,0:04:13.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 它叫小梅
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.36,0:04:19.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是炼丹术吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.60,0:04:23.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,探索流动于大地的力量——龙脉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.76,0:04:25.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并且运用它的法术
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.07,0:04:29.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个刺青结合了我国炼丹术的流派
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.09,0:04:38.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的哥哥不仅研究了炼丹术 还研究了炼金术
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.82,0:04:41.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个刺青就是研究的成果
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.78,0:04:45.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的哥哥是个非常优秀的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.43,0:04:51.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然不知道是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.21,0:04:53.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伤也治好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.20,0:04:56.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就能毫无牵挂地去中央都市了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.29,0:04:59.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样的话 马上就准备吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.21,0:05:03.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 不是叫你快点离开了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.46,0:05:06.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们可不是去玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.51,0:05:08.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是认真的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.72,0:05:11.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才说的不老不死什么的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.64,0:05:13.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能有的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.39,0:05:15.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有的 我就是为此…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.79,0:05:18.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了 小鬼就要像个小鬼…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.79,0:05:24.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用炼丹术是无法实现不老不死的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.67,0:05:27.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是炼金术的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.48,0:05:32.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我必须去拜见传说中的那个人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.47,0:05:36.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,金发加金瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.51,0:05:38.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,红色的大衣 飒爽地披在身上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.11,0:05:42.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,华丽地拯救人们的天才炼金术师
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.00,0:05:45.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱德华·艾尔利克大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.40,0:05:50.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办 老爷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.40,0:05:55.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随便她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.09,0:06:09.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 黑色疾风号
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.98,0:06:16.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么晚一个人走路可是很危险的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.15,0:06:19.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样做的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.24,0:06:24.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是会被我剁碎手巴利袭击的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.93,0:06:30.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然间干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.98,0:06:34.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.83,0:06:37.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样的话 这样如何
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.14,0:06:46.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 为什么没有反应？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.67,0:06:49.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为认识一个类似的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.92,0:06:52.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,类似？是叫阿尔冯斯什么的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.32,0:06:55.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你认识阿尔冯斯君？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.00,0:07:00.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来是那家伙的朋友吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.19,0:07:02.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.39,0:07:05.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好厉害哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.87,0:07:12.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贤者之石
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.04,0:07:16.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到第五研究所和制造石头有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.32,0:07:21.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话 说不定和军队上层也有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.84,0:07:24.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及名叫拉斯多和恩维的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.93,0:07:28.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是他们把你变成这样的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.44,0:07:30.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 是研究人员
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.74,0:07:35.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们强制把我的灵魂拖了出来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.53,0:07:37.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果调查那些研究者的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.61,0:07:40.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许能查出下令做研究的人是什么来历
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.87,0:07:42.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.54,0:07:45.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们也被作为石头的材料了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.55,0:07:47.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个人都没有剩下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.73,0:07:51.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,封口兼做材料吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.13,0:07:53.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是一点都不浪费
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.70,0:07:57.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是否已经没有必要再制造石头了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.76,0:08:01.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后再问你一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.22,0:08:04.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个多月前
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.30,0:08:06.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在中央都市的电话亭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.25,0:08:10.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀害了一个军队将校的是你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.67,0:08:12.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.12,0:08:15.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙被切开了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.44,0:08:18.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.66,0:08:20.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.81,0:08:26.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哟 温莉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.84,0:08:30.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祝你今天心情愉快
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.58,0:08:31.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱德 阿尔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.70,0:08:35.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 突然…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.67,0:08:43.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.10,0:08:47.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帕妮娘现在都在认真工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.77,0:08:48.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帕妮娘吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.55,0:08:51.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放弃了偷盗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.99,0:08:56.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在靠修理房顶之类的工作来生活
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.03,0:08:59.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.21,0:09:01.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有点进展吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.70,0:09:05.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有是有 就是稍微绕了点远路
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.72,0:09:10.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以说是逐渐地进展吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.11,0:09:15.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 那就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.29,0:09:18.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 紧急处理完成
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.98,0:09:20.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢 温莉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.36,0:09:23.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在零件不够 先这样将就一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.68,0:09:24.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.40,0:09:25.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上就调集过来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.95,0:09:27.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们随便走走打发时间吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.45,0:09:29.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话是这样说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.30,0:09:36.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是这里只有机械铠店
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.03,0:09:41.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.57,0:09:43.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.56,0:09:47.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么 捡了只猫吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.36,0:09:49.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.19,0:09:54.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,活过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.69,0:09:56.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们是我的救命恩人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.36,0:09:57.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.70,0:09:58.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢款待
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.27,0:10:00.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没说要请你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.90,0:10:02.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要那么小气嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.81,0:10:03.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不许说“小”
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.88,0:10:07.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 在异国遇见的人情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.53,0:10:08.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是非常难得
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.88,0:10:12.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在异国？你是外国人？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.94,0:10:15.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 从清国来的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.36,0:10:16.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,清是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.81,0:10:19.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,指那个东边的大国？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.85,0:10:20.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.16,0:10:23.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穿越沙漠真是非常辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.57,0:10:25.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要走这种路线
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.32,0:10:29.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为想看看克塞鲁克塞斯遗迹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.68,0:10:32.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克塞鲁克塞斯？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.82,0:10:34.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说那里什么都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.09,0:10:36.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要调查点东西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.29,0:10:40.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来这个国家也是为了调查炼丹术
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.54,0:10:41.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炼丹术？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.03,0:10:45.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个国家叫它炼金术
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.46,0:10:48.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的国家叫它炼丹术
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.91,0:10:51.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是在医学方面的顶尖技术
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.02,0:10:54.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是所谓的国情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.62,0:10:57.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们这里大多用于军事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.59,0:11:01.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在也和南边的阿耶鲁戈 西边的古雷达
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.88,0:11:04.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在国境线附近总是有小冲突
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.93,0:11:07.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,北方也是有大国德拉古马存在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.07,0:11:11.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽说缔结了互不侵犯条约
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.73,0:11:14.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是因为布里克斯山挡在中间而不攻过来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.74,0:11:16.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关系也很糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.11,0:11:18.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是个危险的国家
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.72,0:11:21.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把炼金术广泛用于军事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.12,0:11:25.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是现在的大总统布拉德雷上任以后吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.83,0:11:29.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 我们也很有兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.38,0:11:31.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拥有顶尖医学水平的炼丹术
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.15,0:11:33.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.67,0:11:37.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说你们是炼金术师？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.42,0:11:39.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.29,0:11:40.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是爱德华·艾尔利克
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.20,0:11:42.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,国家炼金术师
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.85,0:11:45.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是他的弟弟 阿尔冯斯·艾尔利克
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.94,0:11:46.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.19,0:11:48.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是姚麟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.89,0:11:49.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.29,0:11:51.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 麟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.40,0:11:54.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,详细地说说炼丹术的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.94,0:11:55.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.89,0:11:58.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是炼丹术师
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.94,0:12:03.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是术师来调查什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.64,0:12:06.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想找个东西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.82,0:12:08.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们会不会知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.87,0:12:11.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贤者之石
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.58,0:12:15.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我非常想要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.31,0:12:17.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.18,0:12:22.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.08,0:12:25.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来知道些什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.98,0:12:30.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能不能告诉我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.77,0:12:33.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想用贤者之石做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.57,0:12:39.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用它获得不老不死的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.61,0:12:48.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能不能告诉我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.77,0:12:51.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真无聊 说什么不老不死
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.83,0:12:52.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是认真的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.62,0:12:57.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不论如何 我可不觉得这是有求于人的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.27,0:12:59.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,态度
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.27,0:13:03.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.14,0:13:06.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也要反抗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.06,0:13:07.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等…等等
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.16,0:13:15.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些家伙会轻功吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.76,0:13:17.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是清国的体术吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.92,0:13:18.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不太好办
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.31,0:13:20.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.35,0:13:22.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起师傅来…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.19,0:13:24.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弱多了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.53,0:13:33.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.83,0:13:37.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大叔 追加甜点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.51,0:13:38.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.81,0:14:05.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.75,0:14:13.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.06,0:14:16.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说什么贤者之石 不老不死
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.84,0:14:18.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然就打起来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.14,0:14:20.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底有什么企图
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.86,0:14:21.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.73,0:14:23.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有那个狐狸眼混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.86,0:14:29.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打中了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.40,0:14:35.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.09,0:14:41.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙 在我骂那个狐狸眼混蛋之后…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.10,0:14:48.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好久不见 帕妮娘
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.72,0:14:50.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底在做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.94,0:14:53.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 基本上猜得到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.39,0:14:54.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 帕妮娘
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.65,0:14:55.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有事拜托你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.79,0:14:57.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.93,0:15:02.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我感觉不到那个铠甲里有活人的气息
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.55,0:15:03.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.37,0:15:09.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得增加人数就有办法了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.15,0:15:11.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愚蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.67,0:15:16.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.12,0:15:18.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,动作被我看穿了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.02,0:15:23.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,部下就这点水平
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.75,0:15:26.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那叫麟的混蛋也就这点程度了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.58,0:15:34.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然 这家伙在主人被辱駡的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.98,0:15:36.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然就失去冷静
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.68,0:15:37.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样一来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.67,0:15:41.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,攻击变得单纯而且动作也大
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.55,0:15:47.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么差不多让我看看…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.50,0:15:50.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的脸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.42,0:15:53.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女人？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.89,0:16:07.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到是义肢内藏炮
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.08,0:16:09.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的不能轻视这个国家
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.32,0:16:12.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.81,0:16:20.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一次的话 也就这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.29,0:16:24.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炼丹术？居然不用阵？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.89,0:16:27.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么…哥哥也没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.77,0:16:34.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干过头了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.30,0:16:37.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.58,0:16:39.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会被麟大人骂的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.08,0:16:47.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 大姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.64,0:16:51.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在大街上居然用这种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.32,0:16:52.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,换了其他人的话 早就死了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.35,0:16:55.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙 自己把手臂…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.26,0:16:59.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小时候经常追兔子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.39,0:17:01.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陷阱可是我的拿手好戏
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.82,0:17:02.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.74,0:17:04.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 阿尔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.09,0:17:06.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.53,0:17:09.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋 居然像没事一样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.41,0:17:11.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们真强
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.10,0:17:15.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样 做我的部下统治一个国家如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.84,0:17:17.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么梦话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.98,0:17:19.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点回清…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.42,0:17:20.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有了 有了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.89,0:17:24.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们居然把城市弄成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.97,0:17:26.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我赔偿
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.41,0:17:28.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,饭钱拿出来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.51,0:17:29.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.21,0:17:33.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,饭钱和赔偿由这小子和他的部下…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.19,0:17:36.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会说这个国家的语言
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.32,0:17:37.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.94,0:17:40.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋 给我站住 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.39,0:17:42.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪 让他逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.03,0:17:45.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边也是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.87,0:17:48.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,惨了 说是修好…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.76,0:17:50.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我现在这副样子…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.92,0:17:53.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行了 哥哥 交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.26,0:17:58.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不需要炼成阵就能炼成了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.28,0:18:02.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概是因为真理的记忆恢复了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.80,0:18:05.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.63,0:18:06.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6\fs60}（天平左：炼金水平 哥哥的威严）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.90,0:18:09.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6\fs60}（天平右：身高）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.83,0:18:12.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6\fs60}（背景字：哥哥的威严）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.52,0:18:14.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后就交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.22,0:18:17.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎 怎么了 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.44,0:18:18.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6\fs60}（背景字：哥哥的威严）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.65,0:18:20.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.37,0:18:23.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哟 又见面了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.32,0:18:26.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还好意思喝茶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.75,0:18:30.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真过份 我们明明是朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.08,0:18:31.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁是你朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.22,0:18:35.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为那两个人 我可是遇到了不少麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.05,0:18:36.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后我会好好教训他们的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.63,0:18:37.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这事就算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.84,0:18:40.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女孩叫兰芳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.95,0:18:42.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老头子叫胡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.60,0:18:45.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们家族世代侍奉我家
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.09,0:18:46.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.96,0:18:50.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蹭饭吃的家伙居然有两个随从
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.51,0:18:52.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身份不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.89,0:18:55.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个嘛 我也算是皇子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.37,0:18:58.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皇子？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.89,0:19:03.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.61,0:19:05.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,王子？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.59,0:19:09.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一般不都吃惊吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.23,0:19:12.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 因为太意外了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.12,0:19:17.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种倒在路边向人蹭饭的家伙居然是皇子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.82,0:19:23.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不允许说麟大人的坏话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.70,0:19:25.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来你在呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.00,0:19:28.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实一点都不显得身份高贵
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.24,0:19:31.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皇子也有很多
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.78,0:19:36.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,清国是由50个民族聚集起来组成的国家
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.21,0:19:39.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由皇帝统治全国
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.31,0:19:44.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后 各民族领袖的女儿嫁给皇帝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.21,0:19:45.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生下小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.93,0:19:48.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在的皇帝有二十四位皇子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.11,0:19:50.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和十九位皇女
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.60,0:19:53.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是这其中的第十二位
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.00,0:19:56.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有四十三个孩子？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.60,0:19:58.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会为了继承权而产生纠纷吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.13,0:20:01.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在就面临这个问题
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.72,0:20:05.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皇帝的身体状况非常不好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.02,0:20:09.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管哪个民族都为了攀上皇位而不择手段
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.07,0:20:11.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.58,0:20:13.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以不老不死的方法为饵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.98,0:20:14.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,攀上皇位
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.03,0:20:15.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,答对了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.36,0:20:18.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以告诉我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.79,0:20:20.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关于贤者之石的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.48,0:20:21.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我拒绝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.83,0:20:24.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贤者之石不是发迹的道具
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.18,0:20:27.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不告诉我的话 就一直跟着你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.32,0:20:28.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别跟过来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.83,0:20:29.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.74,0:20:33.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大街上好像出了乱子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.71,0:20:35.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以回来晚…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.84,0:20:41.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么又掉下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.68,0:20:46.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 你总是 总是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.37,0:20:47.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少主
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.00,0:20:53.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少主没必要给下面的人低头
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.98,0:20:55.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我低个头就能解决的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.11,0:20:57.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也算很便宜了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.23,0:21:01.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可关系到姚族50万人的命运
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.92,0:21:03.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没空管这么多了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.71,0:21:08.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次准备到哪里去弄坏机械铠？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.24,0:21:10.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弄坏为前提吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.30,0:21:13.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想去中央都市调查点事情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.80,0:21:15.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去中央都市吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.45,0:21:18.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想去 想去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.37,0:21:19.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你去干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.54,0:21:22.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去休斯家道谢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.89,0:21:25.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 温莉有工作吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.57,0:21:28.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以哦 温莉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.25,0:21:30.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偶尔也需要放松一下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.38,0:21:31.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.24,0:21:32.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢 伽菲尔先生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.32,0:21:34.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么大家就一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.74,0:21:36.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去中央都市吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.38,0:21:38.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.78,0:21:40.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真让人期待 中央都市
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.62,0:21:45.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以说 你不要跟过来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.71,0:21:51.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果还是跟来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.38,0:21:57.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来 还没问过老爷的名字呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.90,0:22:00.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在可以告诉我了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.33,0:22:02.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊修瓦尔的人民
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.19,0:22:06.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将自己的名字作为神赐的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.43,0:22:07.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,满怀自豪地称呼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.19,0:22:11.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那可真是 老爷肯定也有个非常自豪的…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.58,0:22:13.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我把名字舍弃了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.97,0:22:16.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧 前进
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.42,0:22:18.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.62,0:22:21.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果这是有去无回的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.51,0:22:26.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就舍弃全部神赐之物
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.55,0:24:03.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心中充满对再会的期待
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.30,0:24:05.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回到中央都市的爱德等人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.84,0:24:08.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迎接他们的是悲伤的事实
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.87,0:24:12.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后 黑暗选出了新的祭品
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.57,0:24:16.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下回 钢之炼金术师
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.17,0:24:17.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fullmetal Alchemist
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.88,0:24:21.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第16话 战友的足迹
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.01,0:24:24.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出行的男人心中
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.57,0:24:26.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是光明还是黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.85,0:00:00.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【OP】
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.87,0:01:23.18,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur4}纯白的景色在向我招手
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.21,0:01:29.70,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,1000)\blur4}我即将起程   前往那未知的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.45,0:01:38.67,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}迷茫的旅途
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.70,0:01:41.45,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}在灰色的天空下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.51,0:01:47.56,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}在不断变化的地图里 搀杂着各种梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.56,0:01:49.92,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}总有一天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.96,0:01:54.01,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}即使以我这微小的步伐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.05,0:02:00.04,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}也能走到那云的彼端吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.04,0:02:01.70,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}故作坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.70,0:02:03.21,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}却受了伤
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.33,0:02:06.32,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}仿佛看透了一切
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.32,0:02:07.85,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}从天上落下的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.85,0:02:10.03,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}点点雨水
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.03,0:02:13.24,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}反复的漫反射
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.28,0:02:16.10,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}笔直的光
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.10,0:02:18.82,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}相互交叉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.88,0:02:22.41,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}并不知道去向何方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.41,0:02:23.70,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}只管
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.70,0:02:25.27,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不停地前进
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.33,0:02:31.11,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}淡淡的残影烙印在两眼中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.11,0:02:33.04,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}在这片天空下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.04,0:02:36.88,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}无论身在何处
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.30,0:02:39.16,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}一定可以到达
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.16,0:02:43.97,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1000)\blur4}那未曾见过的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.88,0:00:00.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【ED】
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.55,0:22:34.30,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\fsp-1.5\fnRoman\fs35\b1}Let it all out, Let it all out
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.30,0:22:38.39,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)}不必故作坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.65,0:22:45.17,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,有人这样描绘
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.17,0:22:50.97,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,在墙上涂鸦的花也会摇动
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.97,0:22:56.57,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,没人知道真正的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.57,0:22:58.87,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,在漫长的路途中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.87,0:23:02.27,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,失去与获取
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.27,0:23:09.96,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)}突然寂寞  也有哭泣的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.04,0:23:17.47,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,眼泪也好  痛苦也好  都将化为恒星
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.47,0:23:23.48,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,点燃照亮明天的灯火
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.48,0:23:28.61,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,举起小手  两个人一起创造
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.61,0:23:33.82,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,去搜寻星尘与光芒四射的永远
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.82,0:23:39.19,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,再见 那天也许还会降临
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.19,0:23:45.13,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)}即使季节依然在不断地交替
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.45,0:23:49.21,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,就算有点迷茫  也要向前
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.21,0:23:53.25,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,与你一起前行
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.25,0:23:57.53,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1000)}请让我维持到永远
